Package com.ca.codesv.protocols.http

Provides classes for HTTP protocol.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HttpClientRequest
    Object for transferring request and response between modules.
    HttpConnection
    Specific HTTP Connection implementation, with all necessary information about connection.
    HttpConnection.HttpsConfiguration
    Keystore configuration.
    HttpConnection.HttpsConfigurationBuilder
    Https configuration builder.
    HttpConnectionWrapper
    Wrapper of HttpConnection.
    HttpConstants
    HTTP-related protocol specific constants.
    HttpHeader
    Header object implementation.
    HttpRawBody
    Class representing HTTP raw body of RawRequest and RawResponse.
    HttpRawRequestBuilder
    Transforms HttpServlet request to RequestMessage.
    HttpRequestTransformer
    Transformer used for transforming RawRequest to Request.
    HttpResponseTransformer
    Transformer used for transforming Response to RawResponse.
